A MAN obsessed with snakes was strangled to death by one
of his favourites.According to The
Sun, Dan Brandon (31) was found dead in his room in Fleet, a town west of
London in England, last year.On Wednesday an inquest into his death heard from his mum,
Babs Brandon, how he lived in the family home. In his room, he kept 10 snakes
